Dropsy (c) Devolver Digital

Release Date : 09/2015
Protection : -
Discs : 1
Genre : Adventure
Languages : Multilang

After a deadly circus fire shatters his world and tarnishes his name, Dropsy the Clown finds himself on a journey of self-discovery through a story that harnesses powerful themes of love and kindness. With his father gravely ill and the world turning its back on a once happy-go-lucky clown, Dropsy will need to help those in need, hug total strangers, and unravel dark and shameful secrets from his past on the way to redemption.
